Extract the contaminants protein accessions from a MaxQuant contaminants fasta file

get_maxquant_cont_accessions.Rd

Extract the contaminants protein accessions from a MaxQuant contaminants fasta file

Usage

get_maxquant_cont_accessions(cont_fasta_inf = NULL)

Arguments

cont_fasta_inf

character Filepath to the contaminants fasta. Defaults to NULL in which case, contaminants.fasta.gz from this package will be used

Value

Returns a list of contaminant IDs
